                    <div class="panel-group" id="accordion" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading" role="tab">
      <h4 class="panel-title">
        <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo"><i class="fa fa-building" aria-hidden="true"></i> ABOUT - Danang seaside</a>
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingTwo">
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>The Mother Nature has endowed Da Nang dynamic city with the unique and stunning beauty of beaches.</p>
<p>In 2005, the prestigious American business magazine ֠Forbes named My Khe beach of Da Nang as ԯne of the most attractive beaches on the planetԠtitle.</p>
<p><strong>Irresistible beauty</strong></p>
<p>Voted by American Business Magazine Forbes as one of the six most charming beaches on the planet, My Khe beach attracts thousands of people every year.The Australian magazine, Sunday Herald Sun, also ranked My Khe in the worldӳ top 10 Asian best beaches.</p>
<p class="center">Da Nang beach is an ideal place for sightseeing, swimming and taking photos with beautiful stretches of white smooth sand, its blue water, yellow sunshine and fresh atmosphere as well as poetic ranges of coconut palm trees nearby. What can be greater than sitting on the white smooth sand, enjoy the warm sunshine, the breezes coming from the beach and taking a deep breath? That will be even greater for bathing in cool water with little waves.</p>
<p class="center"><img class="center aligncenter" src="https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_800_800/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAaTAAAAJDUzZTU2NWYzLTEyYjEtNDVmOC04OTFlLTAyZTExMzcwNmQzYg.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="343" data-loading-tracked="true" /></p>
<p class="center" style="text-align: center;"><em>The stunning beauty of My Khe beach &#8211; Photo: goterest.com</em></p>
<p>Moreover, this beach is regarded as a wonderful place for those who want to enjoy the beauty of nature at dawn and twilight. Fresh air, beautiful view at Da Nang beach will help you have huge energy to begin a new day or relax after an exhaust day of working. What a great place to see sunrise and sunset, having great pictures or feeling time passing by!</p>
<p class="center"> <img class="center aligncenter" src="https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_800_800/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAbDAAAAJDZlZmZjMzEzLWRlMTItNGEyMS04ZmQ3LTMzOWNkNDU2MzdmMw.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="252" data-loading-tracked="true" /></p>
<p class="center" style="text-align: center;"><em>Sunset on Da Nang beach &#8211; Photo: panoramio.com</em></p>
<p>From this area, it is easy to watch the gentle statue of lady Buddha named Goddess of Mercy which is 67 meters tall situated on the slope of Son Tra peninsula. Far far away to the southeast lies beautiful Cham islands, a world Biosphere Reserve recognized by UNESCO.</p>
<p>Besides, the beach has coral, abundant plants and creatures along bankside and under sea that is suitable for diving.</p>
<p><strong>And fresh seafood with cheap prices</strong></p>
<p>It will be a shortcoming if visitors forget trying some coastal specialties like shrimps, crabs, fish, and cuttlefishŠWith some visitors wishing to enjoy a meal in a luxurious and quiet space, there is a plenty of high-standard restaurants lying on seaside resorts. However, with those who want to have a meal and enjoy the poetic scene at sunset, it would be perfect to pick one in the row of local food outlets. In those local restaurants, they have all the fresh seafood laid like in the market and visitors have a chance to purchase the raw one as well as select the cooking ways. Foods are extremely delicious, but the price is rather reasonable, for example, a seafood hot pot will cost visitors around $10 for a set of two people.</p>
<p class="center"><img class="center aligncenter" src="https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_800_800/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAPsAAAAJDc4ZmM1MTM2LWI0NjEtNDRkZC04YmUxLTk0ZGM2ZTc4ZTZhNA.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="380" data-loading-tracked="true" /></p>
<p class="center" style="text-align: center;"><em>Seafood &#8211; Photo: The Internet</em></p>
<p><strong>Exciting activities on the beach</strong></p>
<p>With large beach space and slightly waves, the beach is suitable and convenient to play plenty kinds of sports or having activities such as volleyball, fishing, water-skiing, parachute jump, sunbathe, diving, yacht race and so on.</p>
<p class="center" style="text-align: center;"><img class="center" src="https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_800_800/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAPAAAAAJGU0ZDg1OWM3LWE3YmMtNDJjNS05ZWUyLTU2OWM2Y2M4ZGFjOA.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="399" data-loading-tracked="true" /></p>
<p class="center" style="text-align: center;"><em>Enjoy your holiday at My Khe beach &#8211; Photo: danangfoodie.com</em></p>
<p>There are abundant services, creating favorable conditions for you to relax on the seashores including hotels, restaurants, vehicles keeping site, fresh water bathing, sunshade and buoy lease,ż/p>
<p><strong>Safety</strong></p>
<p>Calm seas with little waves,blue water during four seasons, not being polluted with 60% salinization and an annual mean temperature around 25 degrees, slight slope, make it a safe place for both adults and children to go swimming. That the reason why Da Nang Beach is the most crowded and popular to the locals.</p>
<p>Moreover, the safeguard team of Da Nang seashore works from 5 a.m to 8 p.m every day to guarantee safety for visitors to bath and relax on the beach.</p>
<p>In brief, the beach meets all the requirements of a luxurious beach, including easy traffic and access, free admission for tourists, long and flat sand shore, convenience for sea sports, a variety of high-class resorts and international standard villas, said the magazine.</p>
<p>Once you visit Da Nang and come to Da Nang beach, you will want to be back more times because of not only the cityӳ charming beauty, the authentic cuisine, friendly people but also the wonderful beach here. Do not miss it!</p>
